body_html:
the first step to contributing to open source (and you'll get used to this), figure out the steps yourself :)
on a lighter vein, open an issue on https://github.com/pytorch/tutorials and edit the files there, and send a PR on that repo. @chsasank will review it and merge it.

body:
the first step to contributing to open source (and you'll get used to this), figure out the steps yourself :)
on a lighter vein, open an issue on https://github.com/pytorch/tutorials and edit the files there, and send a PR on that repo. @chsasank will review it and merge it.
